{"tid":638761,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"貼「家庭傭工請勿進入游泳池範圍」告示被批歧視　清水灣俱樂部：地方有限　措施可保障訪客安全","createTime":"2018-04-23T04:01:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T06:29:06.000Z","uid":1886,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"feecd784dbe334f2436c4c8b6269517dadd0610d","tid":638761,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T04:01:58.000Z","msg":"近日有網上群組，貼出一張清水灣鄉村俱樂部內的告示，上書「家庭傭工請勿進入游泳池範圍」，被網民質疑歧視。《南華早報》的報道引述俱樂部發言人指，有關措施是因為地方缺乏空間，又指已在泳池附近提供長櫈予傭工。不過報道指，不少會所其實均有類似措施，平機會則指若有人感到受歧視，應向該會尋求協助。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/club_zefnn_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fclub_zefnn_1200x0.png&h=72fad29d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/貼-家庭傭工請勿進入游泳池範圍-告示被批歧視-清水灣俱樂部-地方有限-措施可保障訪客安全/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E8%B2%BC-%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD%E5%82%AD%E5%B7%A5%E8%AB%8B%E5%8B%BF%E9%80%B2%E5%85%A5%E6%B8%B8%E6%B3%B3%E6%B1%A0%E7%AF%84%E5%9C%8D-%E5%91%8A%E7%A4%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%89%B9%E6%AD%A7%E8%A6%96-%E6%B8%85%E6%B0%B4%E7%81%A3%E4%BF%B1%E6%A8%82%E9%83%A8-%E5%9C%B0%E6%96%B9%E6%9C%89%E9%99%90-%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD%E5%8F%AF%E4%BF%9D%E9%9A%9C%E8%A8%AA%E5%AE%A2%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%2F&d=AAE0W%2Bi%2BPuItTZHlspz5jL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=dbef1bfd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E8%B2%BC-%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD%E5%82%AD%E5%B7%A5%E8%AB%8B%E5%8B%BF%E9%80%B2%E5%85%A5%E6%B8%B8%E6%B3%B3%E6%B1%A0%E7%AF%84%E5%9C%8D-%E5%91%8A%E7%A4%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%89%B9%E6%AD%A7%E8%A6%96-%E6%B8%85%E6%B0%B4%E7%81%A3%E4%BF%B1%E6%A8%82%E9%83%A8-%E5%9C%B0%E6%96%B9%E6%9C%89%E9%99%90-%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD%E5%8F%AF%E4%BF%9D%E9%9A%9C%E8%A8%AA%E5%AE%A2%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%2F&h=15c4f0dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/貼-家庭傭工請勿進入游泳池範圍-告示被批歧視-清水灣俱樂部-地方有限-措施可保障訪客安全/</a></div>"},{"pid":"87ef150301197d235aef2a822b182735069fcefd","tid":638761,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T04:02:19.000Z","msg":"一張「家庭傭工請勿進入游泳池範圍」的告示近日被貼上facebook群組「Hong Kong Moms」，隨即惹來網民批評，認為有歧視之嫌。清水灣鄉村俱樂部發言人指，遊泳池並非標準池，故此空間及容量有限，又指已在泳池附近提供長櫈予傭工，以避免過份擠擁及保障所有訪客安全。<br />\n<br />\n不過，有外籍傭工團體認為這是歧視，亦妄顧受傭工照顧的孩子安全。平機會則表示，若有人感到因其種族而被拒使用泳池，可向平機會尋求協助。"},{"pid":"37d6d77fd617bc388f95b8d9299db22f83b6f75f","tid":638761,"uid":152123,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T04:22:18.000Z","msg":"都冇指明種族 依家只係職業歧視姐<br />\n你班工人全部入曬去<br />\n真係唔夠空位"},{"pid":"799b7f95abe4e954ee059eca4d6f0776cbb67eef","tid":638761,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T04:56:40.000Z","msg":"湊住個小朋友咁入唔入得？"},{"pid":"d50c9b59bf3a8a9380ea058668a73204479cb480","tid":638761,"uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T04:58:35.000Z","msg":"想問個場係咩人先入得？係咪之前新聞報嗰啲交平租但唔開俾人用嗰啲閪場？"},{"pid":"3793eba74f85cf3ac6982a79e0bcd96f3d7bd5a1","tid":638761,"uid":27568,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T05:11:04.000Z","msg":"姐姐都有住戶證<br />\n唔認係工人吹得佢脹咩"},{"pid":"62b11af17d401fb4401043ce37330fe5445bd1bf","tid":638761,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T05:17:31.000Z","msg":"公仆呢？"},{"pid":"9757997da7967f2d902f0320b124d7d99c713147","tid":638761,"uid":28580,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T06:29:06.000Z","msg":"之前有單數碼港住戶司機一樣有証,入左會所比人隔一陣CHECK証件一次 19樣...."}]}